+## API Contract
+
+### `GET /api/federation/nodes/stats`
+
+Already exists. Expected response shape (verified against `federation_service.get_aggregated_node_stats`):
+
+**Response 200**
+```json
+{
+  "nodes": {
+    "node-abc": {
+      "hostname": "builder-1.example.com",
+      "os_type": "linux",
+      "status": "online",
+      "last_seen_at": "2026-04-25T10:00:00Z"
+    }
+  },
+  "providers": {
+    "claude": {
+      "success_rate": 0.87,
+      "avg_duration_s": 42.3,
+      "sample_count": 156,
+      "needs_attention": false,
+      "node_count": 2
+    }
+  },
+  "task_types": {
+    "spec": {
+      "claude": {
+        "success_rate": 0.9,
+        "sample_count": 40
+      }
+    }
+  },
+  "alerts": [
+    {
+      "provider": "codex",
+      "metric": "success_rate",
+      "value": 0.42,
+      "threshold": 0.5,
+      "message": "codex success rate 42% < 50% threshold"
+    }
+  ],
+  "window_days": 7,
+  "total_measurements": 312
+}
+```
+
+### `GET /api/federation/nodes/{node_id}/stats`
+
+New endpoint.
+
+**Response 200** (same `providers`, `task_types`, `alerts` shape as above, scoped to one node)
+```json
+{
+  "node_id": "node-abc",
+  "node": {
+    "hostname": "builder-1.example.com",
+    "status": "online"
+  },
+  "providers": {
+    "claude": {
+      "success_rate": 0.87,
+      "avg_duration_s": 42.3,
+      "sample_count": 78,
+      "needs_attention": false
+    }
+  },
+  "task_types": {},
+  "alerts": [],
+  "window_days": 7,
+  "total_measurements": 78
+}
+```
+
+**Response 404**
+```json
+{"detail": "Node not found"}
+```
+
+## Data Model
+
+No new tables. All data comes from `node_measurement_summaries` (written by `store_measurement_summaries`) joined with `federation_nodes`.
+
+```yaml
+# Existing table: node_measurement_summaries
+NodeMeasurementSummaryRecord:
+  id: int
+  node_id: str
+  decision_point: str        # e.g. "provider_spec"
+  slot_id: str               # e.g. "claude", "codex"
+  sample_count: int
+  success_count: int
+  failure_count: int
+  avg_duration_s: float
+  pushed_at: str (ISO 8601)
+  dedup_key: str
+```
